unique_prefixes_total: how many distinct prefixes exist in the app
unique_prefixes_d2: same, but only for that depth
first_party_guess_prefix: heuristic guess of “main app namespace” (I later replaced this guess by using real package from baseline)
obfuscation_score_d3: rough indicator of obfuscation based on weird short namespaces at depth 3
top_prefix_d3_class_count: most frequent depth-3 prefix and its class coverage
